WEBVTT

00:06.499 --> 00:07.840
(Respect copyright)

00:14.112 --> 00:20.704
笙ｪMemories hold you back
from fulfilling your dreams笙ｪ

00:24.288 --> 00:30.432
笙ｪOnly by moving forward
can you find reunion笙ｪ

00:32.640 --> 00:35.872
笙ｪEndings only mark new routes笙ｪ

00:36.096 --> 00:42.112
笙ｪIt's all part of the scenery笙ｪ

00:42.432 --> 00:45.856
笙ｪTo the horizon's call笙ｪ

00:45.920 --> 00:52.480
笙ｪYour journey hasn't started笙ｪ

00:53.536 --> 00:57.472
笙ｪTowards mountains,
chase the stars bright笙ｪ

00:57.472 --> 01:03.552
笙ｪLet time embrace you
and wash away the past笙ｪ

01:03.840 --> 01:07.712
笙ｪPut every twist behind you笙ｪ

01:07.712 --> 01:12.576
笙ｪDrift leisurely through time笙ｪ

01:12.960 --> 01:15.680
笙ｪMake headway against the wind笙ｪ

01:15.680 --> 01:18.667
笙ｪLet mountains bow to your pace笙ｪ

01:18.720 --> 01:24.128
笙ｪRush towards a life without regret笙ｪ

01:24.640 --> 01:28.579
笙ｪLet your nature burst free笙ｪ

01:30.240 --> 01:34.490
=The First Jasmine=

01:35.312 --> 01:37.840
=Episode 31=

01:53.230 --> 01:54.510
Do you remember this?

02:00.071 --> 02:03.664
Back then, when I was being escorted
back to the capital, I ran into you.

02:08.590 --> 02:10.229
You threw me a packet of pastries.

02:12.829 --> 02:14.389
If not for those pastries,

02:16.389 --> 02:18.470
I'd have starved to death
in the prison long ago.

02:25.750 --> 02:26.750
The pastries were gone.

02:28.750 --> 02:30.590
Only the wrapping paper remained.

02:36.069 --> 02:37.229
I couldn't bear to throw it.

02:39.590 --> 02:40.870
So I hid it away.

03:08.304 --> 03:10.704
笙ｪWhy do you panic笙ｪ

03:11.376 --> 03:14.672
笙ｪFor no reason,
you pushed me away and left me笙ｪ

03:15.184 --> 03:17.872
笙ｪAfraid we might start again笙ｪ

03:17.872 --> 03:21.829
笙ｪChanging many things, right or wrong笙ｪ

03:21.829 --> 03:23.024
Your debt is paid.

03:26.710 --> 03:28.669
You need not force yourself

03:30.389 --> 03:32.150
to stay by my side any longer.

03:33.008 --> 03:36.848
笙ｪOur warmth will not be swallowed up笙ｪ

03:37.870 --> 03:39.470
I cannot bear love

03:41.910 --> 03:43.389
offered as charity.

03:44.688 --> 03:46.480
笙ｪThroughout this lifetime笙ｪ

03:46.672 --> 03:51.472
笙ｪIn the end, we're together again笙ｪ

03:51.472 --> 03:54.672
笙ｪCountless trials and pleadings,
right or wrong笙ｪ

03:54.672 --> 03:59.312
笙ｪTry to make this love quiet笙ｪ

03:59.728 --> 04:01.392
笙ｪBut we fight back笙ｪ

04:01.488 --> 04:08.150
笙ｪTo make it a tale to be told笙ｪ

04:08.150 --> 04:09.470
(My virtuous wife, Ye Li:)

04:10.150 --> 04:12.910
(With the matchmaker's help,
we exchanged vows and were wed.)

04:13.509 --> 04:16.390
(Our half-year of marriage
is filled with endless joy.)

04:16.470 --> 04:19.789
(Yet as feelings shifted with time,
goodwill faded and estrangement grew.)

04:20.470 --> 04:21.710
(This is no one's fault.)

04:22.630 --> 04:23.869
(May we part in peace.)

04:24.549 --> 04:25.869
(All your dowry and jewelry)

04:26.189 --> 04:27.349
(will go to you entirely.)

04:28.470 --> 04:29.549
(Land and property deeds)

04:30.590 --> 04:31.749
(are all in your trousseau.)

04:32.989 --> 04:34.109
(After we part ways,)

04:35.270 --> 04:36.549
(may we both find joy)

04:37.309 --> 04:38.549
(and harbor no resentment.)

04:39.349 --> 04:40.510
(The world may turn;)

04:41.150 --> 04:42.349
(this heart will not.)

04:43.590 --> 04:44.749
(Sun and moon bear witness.)

04:44.749 --> 04:46.390
(May we both find joy.)

04:46.390 --> 04:47.549
(This bond is severed.)

04:49.030 --> 04:52.109
(This writ is established,
sealed by life and death.)

04:54.096 --> 04:57.520
笙ｪSilently, we turn pain into joy笙ｪ

04:57.520 --> 04:59.184
笙ｪYou reach out and pull me笙ｪ

04:59.184 --> 05:01.328
笙ｪAnd I gently touch笙ｪ

05:01.328 --> 05:02.800
笙ｪSmooth out the creases笙ｪ

05:02.800 --> 05:06.448
笙ｪSo we can tightly fit together笙ｪ

05:06.448 --> 05:09.648
笙ｪWithout you, there's no me笙ｪ

05:09.648 --> 05:13.808
(Mo Xiuyao)

05:13.808 --> 05:15.984
笙ｪFinds our places in an embrace笙ｪ

05:15.984 --> 05:17.680
笙ｪFulfilling our wishes笙ｪ

05:17.776 --> 05:21.968
笙ｪLovers remain calm and composed笙ｪ

05:23.024 --> 05:24.976
笙ｪLike you, like me笙ｪ

05:25.360 --> 05:28.208
笙ｪIt's like a fond dream笙ｪ

05:28.208 --> 05:33.200
(Tuisi Pavilion)

05:36.848 --> 05:42.512
(Letter of Divorcement.
Ye Li, Mo Xiuyao)

05:54.630 --> 05:56.590
It's so dark in here.

06:01.150 --> 06:03.390
Let me open the door for you.

06:04.189 --> 06:06.470
Staying shut in like this
will make you sick.

06:13.309 --> 06:14.590
Am I crazy?

06:17.590 --> 06:19.510
Why do you say that?

06:23.710 --> 06:25.189
I shouldn't be seeing you.

06:26.749 --> 06:28.669
Only a crazy person can see herself.

06:39.349 --> 06:41.390
You are just too lonely.

06:41.429 --> 06:44.150
You should let Qingshuang stay with you.

06:45.470 --> 06:46.630
But Qingshuang

06:48.390 --> 06:49.710
went back to her hometown.

06:51.590 --> 06:52.710
Mo Xiuyao said

06:53.869 --> 06:55.390
she won't be coming back.

06:56.749 --> 06:57.950
He lied to you.

06:59.030 --> 07:01.030
Qingshuang has come back.

07:06.070 --> 07:06.950
My lady.

07:10.270 --> 07:11.070
Qingshuang,

07:12.950 --> 07:14.070
you're back?

07:15.869 --> 07:18.950
You missed me, so I came back.

07:22.390 --> 07:23.189
Li.

07:29.590 --> 07:32.549
Your eyes are so red. Who upset you?

07:32.950 --> 07:33.830
Tell me.

08:34.224 --> 08:38.256
(To Mo Xiuyao)

08:40.016 --> 08:44.304
笙ｪYou always love with pain笙ｪ

08:45.648 --> 08:51.216
笙ｪForgetting you deserve to be loved too笙ｪ

08:53.510 --> 08:56.469
Your Highness, are you going out
without breakfast?

08:56.750 --> 08:57.630
I'm not eating.

08:58.189 --> 09:00.150
Then, where are you going?

09:00.630 --> 09:01.630
You go ahead.

09:02.230 --> 09:03.030
Yes.

09:05.840 --> 09:09.168
笙ｪYou don't need to chase笙ｪ

09:09.168 --> 09:12.560
笙ｪAfter clouds that winds pursue笙ｪ

09:12.752 --> 09:16.112
笙ｪYou can silently watch each sunrise笙ｪ

09:16.112 --> 09:19.120
笙ｪFinding happiness by your side笙ｪ

09:19.568 --> 09:22.672
笙ｪYou don't need to chart a map笙ｪ

09:22.672 --> 09:26.160
笙ｪOf every bend where love winds on笙ｪ

09:26.512 --> 09:29.648
笙ｪNor travel far to guide its course笙ｪ

09:29.904 --> 09:32.752
笙ｪTo make your heart笙ｪ

09:33.744 --> 09:37.360
笙ｪWarm again笙ｪ

09:48.350 --> 09:49.150
Aunt,

09:50.750 --> 09:51.829
where are you going?

09:53.669 --> 09:54.789
Where are you going, Wuyou?

09:54.789 --> 09:55.669
To school.

09:57.230 --> 09:58.750
Children must study hard.

10:10.390 --> 10:11.309
Let's go.

10:26.789 --> 10:27.589
Your Highness,

10:29.750 --> 10:30.829
Her Highness has left.

10:33.189 --> 10:34.270
(To Mo Xiuyao)
She left this.

10:45.584 --> 10:49.680
笙ｪTime has kept some lines alive笙ｪ

10:51.088 --> 10:56.880
笙ｪThey've recorded of your dreams笙ｪ

10:57.840 --> 10:59.120
(To Mo Xiuyao)

10:59.120 --> 11:04.752
笙ｪHow the snow on the peak
buries the wounds笙ｪ

11:07.030 --> 11:07.829
You're back.

11:09.510 --> 11:10.390
Which one is this?

11:12.189 --> 11:13.510
It's this one.

11:13.789 --> 11:14.589
This one.

11:15.150 --> 11:16.350
Let me see.

11:16.669 --> 11:17.750
Untie this.

11:20.990 --> 11:23.390
Do you want to go in and have a word?

11:25.189 --> 11:26.030
No.

11:30.270 --> 11:32.669
My lady, where are we going then?

11:34.429 --> 11:35.390
Back to Lishan Mountain.

11:35.829 --> 11:36.880
Back to Lishan Mountain?

11:37.429 --> 11:39.469
That's great. I miss the Headmaster.

11:39.469 --> 11:41.429
I miss the masters and seniors too.

11:41.949 --> 11:42.789
I miss them too.

11:44.270 --> 11:45.230
Let's go then.

11:48.669 --> 11:49.589
Let's go.

11:50.736 --> 11:53.360
笙ｪNo need to chase笙ｪ

11:53.936 --> 11:57.232
笙ｪThat quiet and steady happiness笙ｪ

11:57.232 --> 11:58.864
(Shende Shop)

12:00.030 --> 12:00.990
Slow down.

12:09.296 --> 12:10.064
Revenue Clerk Gu.

12:10.960 --> 12:11.760
Revenue Clerk Gu.

12:13.232 --> 12:13.968
Revenue Clerk Gu.

12:14.032 --> 12:15.024
Revenue Clerk Gu.

12:16.350 --> 12:19.270
Revenue Clerk Gu,
you're looking well today.

12:19.469 --> 12:23.429
It seems good news
brings a glow to the spirit.

12:24.990 --> 12:27.110
Revenue Clerk Gu, do you have
some good news to share?

12:29.270 --> 12:32.870
What news could I have
that you haven't already heard?

12:32.870 --> 12:35.350
Judicial Clerk Zhang, aren't you asking

12:36.870 --> 12:38.030
what you already know?

12:42.669 --> 12:44.669
I heard that yesterday,

12:44.750 --> 12:47.750
Zheng Zuoshi's verdict was handed down.

12:51.110 --> 12:52.829
It's a done deal.

12:52.949 --> 12:55.709
He failed his judicial duties,
extorted property,

12:55.709 --> 12:58.096
helped Marquis Muyang forge evidence,

12:58.096 --> 12:59.270
covered up crimes,

12:59.270 --> 13:00.949
withheld Ministry of War documents,

13:00.949 --> 13:02.630
and delayed military dispatches.

13:02.630 --> 13:04.350
He has been sentenced to exile.

13:04.350 --> 13:06.270
All embezzled and bribe money

13:06.270 --> 13:07.949
has been seized.

13:11.150 --> 13:14.829
I heard His Majesty
has sent people to look into officials

13:14.829 --> 13:16.429
tied to Marquis Muyang overnight

13:16.429 --> 13:18.350
and purged over 20 from Imperial Court.

13:18.350 --> 13:19.589
- Over 20 people?
- Over 20 people?

13:19.709 --> 13:21.510
Sun Tingyou, the Vice Minister of Rites,

13:21.910 --> 13:24.669
and He Fangyuan, the Chief Secretary
of War, were also among them.

13:26.709 --> 13:28.949
A large number of court officials
will be replaced.

13:31.350 --> 13:32.368
Military Secretary Wang,

13:33.230 --> 13:37.230
you've rendered
a great service this time.

13:37.230 --> 13:39.549
At the very least,
you're due for a promotion.

13:39.750 --> 13:42.030
When the time comes, don't forget

13:42.030 --> 13:44.270
the bond of our colleagueship.

13:45.189 --> 13:46.709
That's right.

13:46.709 --> 13:47.510
We are colleagues.

13:47.510 --> 13:48.270
Yes.

13:48.949 --> 13:51.549
What are you waiting for?
Want to lose your posts?

13:51.549 --> 13:53.110
Get back to work quickly.

13:54.709 --> 13:55.669
Look at you all.

13:55.669 --> 13:58.110
Enough talk! Have you nothing to do?

13:58.110 --> 13:58.800
Your Highness.

14:05.270 --> 14:06.390
Jin, read the decree.

14:06.549 --> 14:07.309
Yes.

14:10.309 --> 14:11.789
To inherit the grand legacy

14:11.949 --> 14:13.390
and rule over all lands,

14:13.429 --> 14:14.829
the authority to reward and punish

14:14.910 --> 14:16.270
is the foundation of the state.

14:16.549 --> 14:19.469
Regarding the case of Marquis Muyang
and the Huaixi weaponry

14:19.630 --> 14:22.270
and the assassination
of Princess Lingyun of Cangbei,

14:22.270 --> 14:24.309
since the truth is clear,

14:24.469 --> 14:27.150
you officials who have
upheld justice and integrity,

14:27.150 --> 14:28.510
working tirelessly day and night,

14:28.510 --> 14:29.630
shall be promoted

14:29.910 --> 14:31.350
to commend your merits.

14:31.469 --> 14:34.069
Gu Zheng, Revenue Clerk
of Jingzhao Prefecture,

14:34.309 --> 14:35.630
is loyal, diligent,

14:35.910 --> 14:37.150
and meticulous.

14:37.510 --> 14:39.910
He's promoted to Deputy Prefect
of Jingzhao Prefecture

14:40.030 --> 14:41.469
of the Fourth Rank, Junior Lower

14:41.669 --> 14:43.669
to oversee criminal justice
in the capital region

14:43.709 --> 14:45.069
and assist in moral cultivation.

14:45.309 --> 14:48.110
Wang Suwu, Military Secretary
of Jingzhao Prefecture,

14:48.189 --> 14:49.350
strict and fair in commanding

14:49.350 --> 14:50.630
with merit in quelling rebels.

14:50.669 --> 14:52.589
He's now Chief Secretary of War

14:52.669 --> 14:54.789
with the added title
of Closing Court Grand Master

14:54.949 --> 14:57.296
to temporarily serve
the Imperial Court of Judicial Review.

14:57.510 --> 14:59.030
The other officials who contributed

14:59.030 --> 15:00.630
shall each receive 50 bolts of silk

15:00.669 --> 15:01.910
and a one-rank salary raise

15:01.910 --> 15:03.429
to reward their efforts.

15:04.350 --> 15:06.510
We thank His Majesty
for the great grace.

15:11.030 --> 15:13.110
- Congratulations, Deputy Prefect Gu!
- Congratulations!

15:13.110 --> 15:14.589
Likewise. Likewise.

15:16.350 --> 15:18.630
And congratulations
to Chief Secretary Wang.

15:18.630 --> 15:20.429
- Congratulations!
- Congratulations!

15:20.789 --> 15:22.870
See, wasn't my prediction correct?

15:23.910 --> 15:24.750
Quiet!

15:28.150 --> 15:29.390
All of you, get to work!

16:12.880 --> 16:18.128
(Jingzhao Prefecture)

16:26.270 --> 16:28.469
Your Highness, you aren't finished yet?

16:28.870 --> 16:29.669
Is there something?

16:29.829 --> 16:31.390
Indeed, there is something.

16:31.669 --> 16:32.429
Speak.

16:32.429 --> 16:35.429
With Marquis Muyang's fall,
all Jingzhao officials received rewards.

16:35.429 --> 16:38.390
Everyone is in high spirits
and wants to go out and celebrate.

16:42.230 --> 16:43.829
That's only right. You all go ahead.

16:44.270 --> 16:46.549
Your Highness, come join us.

16:47.910 --> 16:49.429
I won't. I still have official duties.

16:50.709 --> 16:53.549
The major case is done. What urgent
official duties could there be?

16:54.469 --> 16:58.189
Your Highness, I just boasted
in front of all of them,

16:58.189 --> 17:00.429
saying I would definitely
be able to invite you

17:00.429 --> 17:01.990
to join us for a couple of drinks.

17:01.990 --> 17:03.350
If Your Highness doesn't go,

17:03.350 --> 17:06.630
I will lose a lot of face
as the new Deputy Prefect.

17:07.110 --> 17:07.910
I said...

17:16.350 --> 17:17.229
You all go on ahead.

17:17.910 --> 17:20.669
I'll come find you
if I get some time later.

17:23.590 --> 17:26.989
Then we shall await Your Highness
at Qingfeng Mingyue Tower.

17:57.136 --> 18:02.256
(Jingzhao Prefecture)

18:24.630 --> 18:25.429
Your Highness,

18:26.749 --> 18:28.590
will you stay here
overnight again today?

18:29.310 --> 18:31.029
You've been busy all day.

18:31.229 --> 18:32.912
You've reviewed all today's documents

18:32.912 --> 18:34.830
and sent up yesterday's. Why don't we...

18:37.429 --> 18:38.949
Why don't we return to the mansion?

18:52.509 --> 18:53.870
To Qingfeng Mingyue Tower.

18:55.310 --> 18:56.110
Let's go.

19:00.630 --> 19:01.429
Impressive!

19:01.749 --> 19:02.870
Fill it up!

19:03.310 --> 19:04.110
Come on!

19:05.310 --> 19:07.189
Ladies, cheers!

19:07.189 --> 19:08.350
- Drink!
- Cheers!

19:20.910 --> 19:22.709
Chief Secretary Wang.

19:26.669 --> 19:27.709
Alright.

19:30.669 --> 19:31.790
His Highness is here.

19:31.870 --> 19:33.509
Quickly, make way.

19:33.509 --> 19:35.269
Make way, make way.

19:35.590 --> 19:37.269
And you all said I was boasting.

19:37.269 --> 19:38.350
His Highness is here. See?

19:38.630 --> 19:39.350
Your Highness.

19:39.350 --> 19:40.229
Quickly.

19:40.229 --> 19:41.509
Your Highness, please come in.

19:41.509 --> 19:43.029
Please have a seat.

19:43.110 --> 19:43.870
Please sit.

19:43.870 --> 19:45.189
Please sit.

19:45.328 --> 19:45.989
Sit.

19:45.989 --> 19:47.189
Your Highness,

19:47.189 --> 19:47.989
I must toast you.

19:47.989 --> 19:48.709
Sit.

19:52.110 --> 19:53.150
Your Highness.

19:53.870 --> 19:55.269
Congratulations, Deputy Prefect Gu.

19:55.269 --> 19:56.350
Thanks to you.

20:01.429 --> 20:03.870
Your Highness, I want to toast you too.

20:04.910 --> 20:06.029
I shall go first.

20:09.776 --> 20:11.229
Your Highness, let me fill your cup.

20:11.229 --> 20:12.949
Let me fill your cup.

20:13.390 --> 20:14.229
Come on.

20:19.550 --> 20:21.350
Why aren't you all
hurrying over to toast?

20:23.408 --> 20:24.112
Cheers!

20:26.320 --> 20:27.920
Come on. Good wine!

20:29.168 --> 20:29.936
Good wine!

21:38.110 --> 21:39.229
I'll do it myself.

21:40.240 --> 21:40.920
Your Highness.

21:42.799 --> 21:43.440
Your Highness.

21:50.200 --> 21:51.200
Be careful.

22:01.160 --> 22:03.319
Don't bother with me. You can go.

22:05.039 --> 22:08.160
Your Highness, I'll fetch some water
for you to wash your face.

22:10.000 --> 22:11.279
No need.

22:11.720 --> 22:12.970
Just go.

22:13.200 --> 22:14.160
Thank you.

22:28.160 --> 22:31.559
Li. Li.

22:34.346 --> 22:36.240
(When you're away, you must be careful.)

22:36.240 --> 22:38.282
Don't stand for too long, run or jump.

22:38.282 --> 22:39.319
Don't engage in fights.

22:39.319 --> 22:40.880
And don't act recklessly again.

22:41.279 --> 22:43.519
(Starting today,
you no longer need to take medicine.)

22:43.839 --> 22:46.799
This room is too dark.
It needs some light.

22:47.599 --> 22:49.962
Then, drink this soup up.

22:50.640 --> 22:52.200
Or I have to reheat it when it cools.

22:54.240 --> 22:56.559
Could you come back
and join us for dinner?

23:01.640 --> 23:03.200
Let's eat, Li.

23:10.039 --> 23:11.839
I'm sorry. I'm sorry.

23:12.880 --> 23:14.680
I'm sorry. I'm sorry.

23:17.200 --> 23:18.319
I'm sorry.

23:31.480 --> 23:32.279
Li?

23:33.920 --> 23:34.720
Li?

23:39.119 --> 23:39.920
Li?

23:44.400 --> 23:46.122
I bought you

23:46.440 --> 23:50.039
the Eight-Treasure Duck
from Qingfeng Mingyue Tower.

23:50.920 --> 23:52.160
Eat it while it's hot.

23:55.400 --> 23:56.200
Where are you?

24:00.960 --> 24:01.880
No rush.

24:03.640 --> 24:07.640
Actually, I also brought you
two packs of candy.

24:10.759 --> 24:13.759
Still no rush.
I'll put them away for you first.

24:15.920 --> 24:17.000
Where's the candy jar?

24:18.160 --> 24:20.640
Can you tell me
where you put your candy jar?

24:54.359 --> 24:55.400
Found it.

25:33.640 --> 25:34.440
Li,

25:38.720 --> 25:40.880
I'll put them in one by one for you,

25:41.720 --> 25:43.480
and you can eat them one by one.

25:45.920 --> 25:47.559
You can eat the candy slowly.

25:49.240 --> 25:51.480
But the Eight-Treasure Duck
can't sit out for too long.

25:53.240 --> 25:55.000
You can come out now.

26:03.000 --> 26:04.039
Still hiding?

26:06.359 --> 26:09.799
Alright, I'll wait for you.

26:15.216 --> 26:16.519
I'll wait for you.

26:21.400 --> 26:22.400
Li,

26:25.599 --> 26:26.440
don't hide.

26:31.039 --> 26:32.119
I miss you.

26:46.160 --> 26:46.960
My lady!

26:57.480 --> 26:58.279
Your Highness.

27:06.079 --> 27:06.880
Your High...

27:08.640 --> 27:12.079
Your Highness, I'll go prepare
some breakfast first.

27:36.112 --> 27:38.288
(To Master Zhu, Lishan Academy)

27:41.720 --> 27:42.640
Eat your soup.

27:42.640 --> 27:43.759
You may go.

27:44.960 --> 27:45.880
You have to rewrite.

27:47.599 --> 27:49.000
Let me.

27:52.920 --> 27:54.160
Luckily, the inside isn't wet.

27:55.400 --> 27:58.480
Just sit tight and don't make trouble.

28:03.480 --> 28:04.279
You may leave.

28:09.759 --> 28:10.839
Yes.

28:20.720 --> 28:21.520
(To Grandfather, Lishan Academy)

28:21.520 --> 28:22.672
(To Master Helai, Lishan Academy)

28:22.672 --> 28:24.240
(To He Minghui)

28:24.240 --> 28:25.072
(To Senior Zhang Yu, Lishan Academy)

28:25.072 --> 28:26.736
(To Senior Feng Yang, Lishan Academy)

28:26.736 --> 28:27.600
(To Senior Cen Can, Lishan Academy)

28:30.288 --> 28:32.336
(To Master Zhu, Lishan Academy)

28:36.960 --> 28:38.359
(Master Zhu,)

28:38.559 --> 28:41.480
(a month has flown by
since I left the mountain.)

28:42.200 --> 28:44.279
(I still recall
your fondness for sweets.)

28:45.039 --> 28:46.720
(I've collected dew from linden buds)

28:47.000 --> 28:48.400
(and brewed it the old way.)

28:48.559 --> 28:50.559
(I humbly hope you may enjoy it.)

29:03.344 --> 29:03.920
(Dear Grandfather)

29:03.920 --> 29:06.039
(I wonder if you're in good health)

29:06.799 --> 29:08.880
(or if your old migraine has recurred.)

29:09.240 --> 29:10.519
(Take great care of yourself.)

29:19.039 --> 29:20.519
For Xiuyao's leg medication,

29:20.680 --> 29:22.839
(Master Helai)
the dosage and timing must be precise.

29:23.480 --> 29:25.279
I've attached the prescription.

29:25.359 --> 29:27.039
Please examine it, master,

29:27.039 --> 29:28.559
to set my mind at ease.

29:44.599 --> 29:45.400
Zhuang.

29:45.960 --> 29:46.759
Your Highness?

29:47.000 --> 29:48.359
Li has a senior named Li Feibai.

29:48.359 --> 29:50.319
Where is he? How can I find him?

29:50.839 --> 29:52.319
You're looking for Li Feibai?

29:52.359 --> 29:53.079
Yes.

30:02.200 --> 30:03.160
Where is Li Feibai?

30:03.960 --> 30:04.759
Where is Li Feibai?

30:04.759 --> 30:05.319
Second floor.

30:23.920 --> 30:24.799
It's you.

30:27.279 --> 30:28.400
You're Li's senior.

30:28.799 --> 30:29.599
What is it?

30:30.119 --> 30:31.119
I have questions for you.

30:32.960 --> 30:34.319
Li wrote so many letters.

30:34.720 --> 30:36.240
Why were none of them sent out?

30:37.000 --> 30:39.880
Look, they're for Headmaster Xu

30:40.519 --> 30:41.960
and various masters.

30:42.440 --> 30:44.200
So many of them, and none were sent.

30:44.839 --> 30:45.960
She made some flower nectar.

30:46.200 --> 30:47.480
She said it was for Master Zhu,

30:47.640 --> 30:49.400
but the nectar is still in the mansion.

30:49.640 --> 30:51.240
And Senior He's father

30:51.480 --> 30:53.799
wrote a family letter,
entrusting Li to pass it on.

30:53.920 --> 30:54.920
Now it's here too.

30:56.319 --> 30:57.119
Why?

30:59.680 --> 31:02.200
Where is Li? Where is she?

31:05.759 --> 31:07.240
I'm asking you. Where is Li?

31:12.279 --> 31:13.200
She left.

31:13.200 --> 31:14.200
Left?

31:15.359 --> 31:16.000
Why?

31:17.599 --> 31:18.519
Where did she go?

31:22.279 --> 31:23.640
You drove her away?

31:26.640 --> 31:27.599
Answer me.

31:28.079 --> 31:29.480
Did you drive her away?

31:29.640 --> 31:30.799
Did she go back to Lishan?

31:35.480 --> 31:36.920
Mo Xiuyao,

31:37.400 --> 31:38.640
since Li left the mountain,

31:39.200 --> 31:41.599
she has spared no effort
in healing your legs

31:42.039 --> 31:43.920
and clearing the name of your household.

31:44.240 --> 31:45.200
But what about you?

31:46.200 --> 31:47.839
Is this how you repay her?

31:50.039 --> 31:51.720
What did you promise her?

31:52.640 --> 31:54.928
You said you'd never leave her,
no matter what.

31:54.928 --> 31:56.200
And what about now?

31:58.680 --> 32:00.319
You drove her back to Lishan,

32:00.960 --> 32:04.039
leaving her alone
on a desolate mountain.

32:10.799 --> 32:14.039
What do you mean, leaving her alone
on a desolate mountain?

32:15.480 --> 32:16.480
What happened at Lishan?

32:18.400 --> 32:19.640
What happened at Lishan?

32:23.160 --> 32:24.839
Haven't you found out long ago?

32:25.519 --> 32:27.000
Why else would you come to me?

32:29.319 --> 32:30.240
I found out?

32:32.799 --> 32:33.839
What did I find out?

32:34.359 --> 32:36.480
You've been with Li
day and night for so long.

32:38.160 --> 32:40.000
Don't you know about Qingshuang?

32:44.839 --> 32:45.720
Qingshuang?

32:51.319 --> 32:52.880
(Since you know about Qingshuang,)

32:53.480 --> 32:56.480
(you should understand
what happened on Lishan Mountain.)

33:02.544 --> 33:03.472
(He Minghui)

33:20.519 --> 33:23.200
(I'm writing to my grandfather,
the masters,)

33:23.519 --> 33:25.240
and the seniors at Lishan Mountain.

33:25.960 --> 33:27.920
It's been a long while
since I last saw them.

33:27.920 --> 33:30.400
They all must be missing me.

33:31.056 --> 33:34.079
(To Master Zhu, Lishan Academy)

33:34.079 --> 33:37.240
(Do you still feel lonely
living in the mansion now?)

33:37.720 --> 33:40.240
No. Plenty of people
are in the mansion, after all.

33:40.519 --> 33:41.799
Why, Your Highness?

33:42.992 --> 33:44.359
You never feel lonely?

33:44.680 --> 33:45.480
That's right.

33:45.960 --> 33:47.039
And in the Lishan Academy?

33:48.000 --> 33:48.799
Lishan Academy?

33:50.319 --> 33:51.599
So many people are there.

33:51.680 --> 33:55.039
Once I wake up,
I'll spend hours just on meals,

33:55.599 --> 33:57.920
leaving me scarce time for rest.

33:57.960 --> 33:59.119
No time for loneliness.

34:04.160 --> 34:05.160
(Your hand is so cold.)

34:06.440 --> 34:07.519
(Are you very cold?)

34:07.839 --> 34:11.360
When I was on Lishan Mountain, I often
couldn't sleep because of the cold.

34:12.519 --> 34:14.119
Qingshuang always held me to sleep.

34:14.119 --> 34:17.360
The moon above Lishan Mountain
is so big.

34:18.880 --> 34:21.079
Lying in the courtyard every night,

34:22.000 --> 34:24.639
I felt as if it was embracing me.

34:29.440 --> 34:30.679
(I love eating candy.)

34:31.239 --> 34:33.360
(But on Lishan Mountain,
there was no candy.)

34:37.760 --> 34:39.199
(Mo Xiuyao,)

34:40.440 --> 34:42.079
(you drove her back to Lishan,)

34:42.800 --> 34:45.880
(leaving her alone
on a desolate mountain.)

35:18.480 --> 35:21.199
Your Highness? Your Highness?

35:30.199 --> 35:31.039
Are you in there?

35:32.679 --> 35:33.280
(To Grandfather, Lishan Academy)
Come in.

35:35.880 --> 35:37.920
Your Highness, are we still going...

35:42.199 --> 35:43.639
to the prefectural office today?

35:46.440 --> 35:49.679
Or shall I request a leave of absence
on your behalf?

35:50.800 --> 35:51.639
Help me wash up.

35:56.592 --> 35:58.239
(Qiongying Residence)

35:58.239 --> 36:00.480
My lady, His Highness
is already waiting outside.

36:12.360 --> 36:13.159
Yao?

36:22.639 --> 36:25.880
Yao, you... What happened to you?

36:26.960 --> 36:30.079
Ms. Wen, I must leave for a while.

36:31.480 --> 36:32.519
Where are you going?

36:33.239 --> 36:34.079
To Lishan Mountain.

36:35.280 --> 36:38.760
Lishan Mountain? Are you going
to find Li and bring her back?

36:39.199 --> 36:40.000
Yes.

36:40.639 --> 36:42.199
Good.

36:43.320 --> 36:46.679
But Lishan Mountain is heavily guarded,
and no one can enter without a decree.

36:47.599 --> 36:49.000
How can you get up there?

36:49.360 --> 36:51.920
Besides, the Jingzhao Prefect
oversees the capital's safety.

36:52.239 --> 36:54.559
Will His Majesty allow you
to leave for a long time?

36:54.639 --> 36:57.519
I shall petition His Majesty
to release me from my post.

36:57.639 --> 37:00.440
I will also request a pass
to enter the mountain.

37:01.320 --> 37:04.960
No matter what,
I must go up Lishan Mountain.

37:06.360 --> 37:09.280
Alright, go then.

37:12.719 --> 37:13.456
Yao,

37:15.536 --> 37:17.360
you must take good care of yourself.

37:18.599 --> 37:20.400
You are still so young.

37:24.368 --> 37:25.679
Ms. Wen, don't worry.

37:28.639 --> 37:29.360
Go.

38:00.079 --> 38:01.280
What has happened to you?

38:01.639 --> 38:04.199
It's only been a few days,
and you've become like this?

38:05.960 --> 38:07.079
Thank you for your concern.

38:08.760 --> 38:12.159
My father also developed
gray hair at a young age.

38:12.599 --> 38:14.039
It's an inherited condition.

38:14.679 --> 38:16.960
And time does its part too.

38:18.239 --> 38:19.519
Your Majesty need not worry.

38:20.840 --> 38:22.760
What is the purpose of your visit?

38:24.760 --> 38:28.440
I humbly beseech Your Majesty
to grant me an imperial pass

38:28.960 --> 38:30.280
to ascend Lishan Mountain.

38:31.239 --> 38:33.920
You want to go up Lishan Mountain? Why?

38:34.159 --> 38:34.960
Your Majesty,

38:37.679 --> 38:39.320
I had a quarrel with my wife.

38:40.079 --> 38:42.159
My rude words hurt her heart.

38:42.960 --> 38:45.239
In her grief, she returned
to Lishan Mountain.

38:45.840 --> 38:48.480
But Lishan Mountain
is still under lockdown.

38:48.960 --> 38:51.719
She can return, but I cannot go up.

38:53.280 --> 38:54.559
I have no other choice.

38:55.800 --> 38:58.760
I could only come
to beg Your Majesty for grace.

39:09.320 --> 39:11.679
I do not know when
I will return from this trip.

39:12.679 --> 39:14.840
Jingzhao Prefecture's affairs
are immense.

39:15.679 --> 39:18.079
Deputy Prefect Gu Zheng
is diligent and capable.

39:18.559 --> 39:21.040
He can temporarily manage
the routine matters.

39:22.840 --> 39:23.639
Also,

39:27.559 --> 39:29.480
since I assumed
the post of Jingzhao Prefect,

39:30.159 --> 39:32.920
I've been lacking in talent and virtue,
with mediocre achievements.

39:33.400 --> 39:36.519
Coupled with my chronic illness,
my energy is insufficient.

39:36.960 --> 39:38.320
I fear I may fail Your Majesty.

39:39.639 --> 39:42.840
I implore Your Majesty
to find a worthy replacement

39:43.599 --> 39:46.800
and let me step down
as Jingzhao Prefect.

40:03.079 --> 40:04.320
Mother, you have no idea.

40:04.719 --> 40:06.079
In just a few days' time,

40:06.199 --> 40:08.920
Xiuyao's hair has turned
completely gray, like an old man.

40:09.679 --> 40:11.039
When I asked him the reason,

40:11.280 --> 40:13.440
he just said
it was a hereditary condition.

40:14.320 --> 40:15.360
I remember

40:15.519 --> 40:18.119
his father indeed had hair
as white as snow

40:18.400 --> 40:19.840
before he turned fifty.

40:20.400 --> 40:22.920
But Xiuyao is in his prime,
not yet thirty.

40:23.280 --> 40:24.559
This is far too early.

40:26.199 --> 40:28.239
Right. During his audience today,

40:28.480 --> 40:30.320
he requested
to resign as Jingzhao Prefect.

40:31.119 --> 40:31.920
Resign?

40:32.480 --> 40:33.320
Yes.

40:34.280 --> 40:36.360
He said he quarreled with his wife

40:36.880 --> 40:38.679
and wanted to find her
on Lishan Mountain.

40:46.159 --> 40:47.679
That sounds like an excuse.

40:48.360 --> 40:50.320
The Marquis Muyang case has just ended.

40:50.440 --> 40:52.159
Now the court is in a state of unrest.

40:53.079 --> 40:54.119
I am worried

40:54.199 --> 40:57.119
that Prince Ding choosing this moment
to resign from a key capital post

40:57.400 --> 40:58.920
could be a strategic retreat.

40:59.320 --> 41:02.480
Could there be more to this move
by the couple than meets the eye?

41:03.280 --> 41:05.280
It's not necessarily an excuse.

41:06.559 --> 41:07.960
During Prince Ding's audience,

41:08.119 --> 41:11.280
aside from his hair,
was his demeanor or complexion off?

41:12.320 --> 41:13.519
When he came this morning,

41:13.960 --> 41:16.320
his brow was heavy with pain and sorrow,

41:16.880 --> 41:20.360
as if his wife's return
to Lishan Mountain this time

41:20.480 --> 41:22.239
was due to some catastrophic event.

41:23.079 --> 41:26.119
If you have doubts, just send someone
to find out the truth.

41:28.159 --> 41:29.480
Issue my decree.

41:33.800 --> 41:35.920
Prince Ding is now
the Pacification Commissioner

41:36.360 --> 41:38.159
and granted a banner of authority.

41:38.400 --> 41:40.480
He shall bring 50 bolts of silk,
100 taels of gold,

41:40.480 --> 41:41.920
and a box of century-old ginseng

41:42.360 --> 41:44.760
to visit Lishan on behalf of His Majesty

41:45.079 --> 41:46.480
to demonstrate the imperial grace.

41:48.320 --> 41:51.159
Shunxi, accompany
Prince Ding on this trip.

41:51.360 --> 41:52.159
Yes.

41:53.400 --> 41:55.039
Sir, bring some flatbread over.

41:55.039 --> 41:55.679
Alright.

42:00.039 --> 42:01.039
Here you go.

42:03.360 --> 42:07.119
Wait. It's one thing
not to have pastries here,

42:07.440 --> 42:09.239
but don't you even have any hot dishes?

42:11.408 --> 42:11.952
Sir,

42:13.072 --> 42:15.559
you can barely see anyone on this road.

42:16.280 --> 42:19.079
Having a bowl of hot noodle soup
from me is already a rare find.

42:20.240 --> 42:21.760
Even some spiced meat would do.

42:22.360 --> 42:24.239
This soup of yours is so watery.

42:24.239 --> 42:27.079
I can see my reflection in it.
How am I supposed to eat this?

42:27.559 --> 42:29.440
Any random street stall in the capital

42:29.440 --> 42:30.639
has spiced meat on hand.

42:31.920 --> 42:33.079
Sir, you jest.

42:33.119 --> 42:36.079
How can my little stall compare
to any shop in the capital?

42:36.320 --> 42:38.760
How about I add some more
chopped scallions for you?

42:41.072 --> 42:43.920
(Preview)

42:44.800 --> 42:48.079
Imperial Pacification Commissioner
Prince Ding has come to pay a visit.

42:49.199 --> 42:50.519
Why is there no one here at all?

42:50.880 --> 42:53.599
If they're not at the academy,
where else could they be?

42:53.920 --> 42:55.199
I'm sorry, Li.

42:55.599 --> 42:58.000
Yao, what exactly happened?

42:58.599 --> 42:59.679
The entire Lishan Mountain

42:59.719 --> 43:02.079
has no one else except you.

43:02.840 --> 43:03.679
No one?

43:04.920 --> 43:07.280
How could there be no one?

43:14.736 --> 43:21.328
笙ｪMemories hold you back
from fulfilling your dreams笙ｪ

43:24.912 --> 43:31.056
笙ｪOnly by moving forward
can you find reunion笙ｪ

43:33.264 --> 43:36.496
笙ｪEndings only mark new routes笙ｪ

43:36.720 --> 43:42.736
笙ｪIt's all part of the scenery笙ｪ

43:43.056 --> 43:46.480
笙ｪTo the horizon's call笙ｪ

43:46.544 --> 43:53.104
笙ｪYour journey hasn't started笙ｪ

43:54.160 --> 43:58.096
笙ｪTowards mountains,
chase the stars bright笙ｪ

43:58.096 --> 44:03.792
笙ｪBoth joy and grief
make the trip worthwhile笙ｪ

44:04.304 --> 44:12.912
笙ｪTrying to catch up
to your own lost shadow笙ｪ

44:13.808 --> 44:19.312
笙ｪWithin the wilds, echoes thrive笙ｪ

44:19.312 --> 44:24.816
笙ｪClear mind leads to a clear path笙ｪ

44:24.880 --> 44:28.944
笙ｪBe grateful to your losses笙ｪ

44:29.232 --> 44:34.456
笙ｪMake your steps weightless笙ｪ

44:35.056 --> 44:38.768
笙ｪTowards mountains,
chase the stars bright笙ｪ

44:38.800 --> 44:44.464
笙ｪLet time embrace you
and wash away the past笙ｪ

44:45.232 --> 44:53.200
笙ｪPut every twist behind you,
drift leisurely through time笙ｪ

44:54.608 --> 44:59.856
笙ｪMake headway against the wind,
let mountains bow to your pace笙ｪ

45:00.112 --> 45:06.016
笙ｪRush towards a life without regret笙ｪ

45:06.016 --> 45:10.136
笙ｪLet your nature burst free笙ｪ

45:10.352 --> 45:15.088
笙ｪUnbound by form笙ｪ

45:16.304 --> 45:20.576
笙ｪLet your nature burst free笙ｪ

45:20.816 --> 45:26.256
笙ｪUnbound by form笙ｪ
